- Removed following extensions:
    crack, db, domxml, fribidi, mcal, overload, qtdom, zip
  They were either moved to PECL, or permanently removed.
- Added following extensions
    tidy, simplexml
  They are build by default, but can be disabled by using bcond.
- Hyperwave extension depends on proprietary libs, thus it is not being
  built by default
- Removed obsolete BuildRequires
- Removed obsolete patches, sorted the rest
- OpenSSL extensions is now build as a module (it was broken in 4.3.x)
- /php 4/php 5/ in some of summaries
- Added %{_pre} to Release
- Some cosmetics in bcond descriptions
- Almost done, sybase module still doesn't build.
